{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":914,"text":"Good afternoon."},{"time":2241,"text":"My name is Uldus."},{"time":3782,"text":"I am a photo-based artist from Russia."},{"time":7755,"text":"I started my way around six years ago"},{"time":10784,"text":"with ironic self-portraits"},{"time":13810,"text":"to lay open so many stereotypes"},{"time":16780,"text":"about nationalities, genders,"},{"time":20222,"text":"and social issues —"},{"time":21662,"text":"[\"I am Russian. I sell drugs, guns, porno with kids!\"]\n[\"Vodka = water. I love vodka!\"] (Laughter) —"},{"time":24665,"text":"using photography as my tool to send a message.\n[\"Marry me, I need a visa.\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29233,"text":"Today, I am still performing in front of the camera"},{"time":32315,"text":"and trying to be brave like Wonder Woman."},{"time":36162,"text":"I focus on balancing meaningful message,"},{"time":39840,"text":"aesthetic, beauty, composition, \nsome irony, and artifacts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45870,"text":"Today, I'm going to tell you about my project,"},{"time":49312,"text":"which is named Desperate Romantics."},{"time":52271,"text":"They're my artifacts, or paintings"},{"time":53989,"text":"from pre-Raphaelites Brotherhood England"},{"time":58817,"text":"mid-19th century."},{"time":60926,"text":"I took the painting"},{"time":62940,"text":"and gifted new, contemporary meaning"},{"time":66182,"text":"talking about issues which are surrounding me"},{"time":70037,"text":"in Russia,"},{"time":71377,"text":"capturing people who are non-models"},{"time":74698,"text":"but have an interesting story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77780,"text":"This boy is a professional dancer,"},{"time":79929,"text":"only 12 years old,"},{"time":81512,"text":"but at secondary school, he hides his dancing classes"},{"time":85440,"text":"and is wearing the mask of brutality,"},{"time":87821,"text":"trying to be united with the rest of his classmates"},{"time":92145,"text":"like a storm trooper has no personality."},{"time":94877,"text":"But this boy has goals and dreams"},{"time":97577,"text":"but hides it to be socially accepted,"},{"time":100570,"text":"because being different isn't easy,"},{"time":103218,"text":"especially in Russia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105515,"text":"Next portrait interpretation is metaphoric."},{"time":109261,"text":"And this is Nikita,"},{"time":111376,"text":"a security guard from one of the bars"},{"time":114740,"text":"in St. Petersburg."},{"time":116607,"text":"He likes to say, \"You wouldn't like me when I'm angry,\""},{"time":120207,"text":"quoting Hulk from the movie,"},{"time":122198,"text":"but I've never seen him angry."},{"time":124442,"text":"He hides his sensitivities and romantic side,"},{"time":127947,"text":"because in Russia, among guys,"},{"time":129938,"text":"that's not cool to be romantic,"},{"time":131772,"text":"but it's cool to be surrounded with women"},{"time":134520,"text":"and look like an aggressive hulk."},{"time":136823,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139100,"text":"Sometimes, in my project,"},{"time":141480,"text":"I would take the painting"},{"time":143350,"text":"and give it new meaning"},{"time":146205,"text":"and new temptation about it."},{"time":149040,"text":"Sometimes, I would compare facial features"},{"time":152572,"text":"and playing with words:"},{"time":154858,"text":"irony, Iron Man, ironing man."},{"time":159232,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162527,"text":"Through the artifacts,"},{"time":164020,"text":"I bring social issues"},{"time":166100,"text":"which surround me in Russia into the conversation."},{"time":169806,"text":"Interesting fact about marriage in Russia,"},{"time":172809,"text":"that most of the 18, 19-year-old girls"},{"time":176285,"text":"are already ready, and dream to get married."},{"time":179525,"text":"We're taught from childhood,"},{"time":181100,"text":"successful marriage means successful life,"},{"time":184385,"text":"so most of the girls kind of fight"},{"time":186949,"text":"to get a good husband."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189534,"text":"And what about me?"},{"time":191787,"text":"I'm 27 years old."},{"time":193822,"text":"For Russian society, I'm an old maid"},{"time":196703,"text":"and hopeless to ever get married."},{"time":199526,"text":"That's why you see me in a Mexican fighter mask,"},{"time":202822,"text":"in the wedding dress, all desperate in my garden."},{"time":207209,"text":"But remember, irony is the key,"},{"time":209930,"text":"and this is actually to motivate girls"},{"time":212283,"text":"to fight for goals, for dreams,"},{"time":215185,"text":"and change stereotypes."},{"time":218481,"text":"Be brave. Be ironic — it helps."},{"time":221823,"text":"Be funny and create some magic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225962,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}